The final result should become a **complete blueprint for building the MockTrial.app platform**, including:

* courtroom simulation engine
* AI courtroom role system
* multiplayer classroom infrastructure
* legal rules engine
* spectator reconstruction tools

The platform will ultimately function as:

* a legal education platform
* a collaborative simulation environment
* a multiplayer educational game
* a courtroom training tool.

